nodes.text: Kels was a male Human who served as the chief engineer aboard the Dorin's Sky, a Thranta-class corvette in the Republic Navy. During the Galactic War, the Dorin's Sky was boarded by the reconstituted Sith Empire, and Kels was killed defending the engineering deck.
Chief Engineer Kels appears as one of the bosses in the Boarding Party Flashpoint appearing in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
